<section class="problem">
  <div class="problem-inner">

    <figure class="problem-media">
      <img
        src="{{ 'br-technique-diagram.webp' | asset_url }}"
        alt="Gua sha technique diagram showing how the stroke path lifts brows, depuffs the under-eye, contours cheeks, and defines the jawline"
        loading="lazy"
      >
    </figure>

    <div class="problem-copy">
      <p class="problem-eyebrow">Sound Familiar?</p>

      <h2 class="problem-title">You wake up looking<br><span class="problem-title-accent">more tired than you feel.</span></h2>

      <ul class="problem-list">
        <li>Your face is puffy. Every morning. No matter how much water you drank or how early you went to bed.</li>
        <li>Your jawline has softened. You see it in photos. You don't say anything but you notice.</li>
        <li>You've spent money on serums, creams, eye patches. Your skin still looks the same at 7am.</li>
        <li>You want to look like yourself — just the best version. Without a full makeup routine before 8am.</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="problem-pivot">
        <span class="problem-pivot-lead" aria-hidden="true">—</span>
        The problem isn't your skin. It's that no cream can physically move fluid, drain puffiness, or lift facial muscles. Only mechanical stimulation can do that. That's what gua sha is.
      </p>

      <a href="#shop" class="problem-cta">Start the Ritual</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
.problem {
  background: var(--cream);
  padding: var(--space-section-y) var(--space-section-x);
}
.problem-inner {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: clamp(48px, 7vw, 100px);
  align-items: center;
}

/* Media */
.problem-media {
  margin: 0;
}
.problem-media img {
  width: 100%;
  aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
  object-fit: cover;
  display: block;
}

/* Copy column */
.problem-copy {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}
.problem-eyebrow {
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.4em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--terracotta);
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}
.problem-title {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: clamp(32px, 3.6vw, 52px);
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.1;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  color: var(--espresso);
  margin: 0 0 clamp(28px, 4vw, 44px);
}
.problem-title-accent {
  color: var(--terracotta);
}

/* Pain list */
.problem-list {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0 0 clamp(32px, 4vw, 44px);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 20px;
}
.problem-list li {
  position: relative;
  padding-left: 28px;
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: clamp(15px, 1.3vw, 17px);
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: var(--espresso);
  max-width: 54ch;
}
.problem-list li::before {
  content: '—';
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  top: 0;
  font-family: var(--serif);
  color: var(--terracotta);
  font-size: 1em;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* Pivot paragraph — editorial pull-quote, no bordered box */
.problem-pivot {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: clamp(17px, 1.5vw, 20px);
  line-height: 1.55;
  color: var(--espresso);
  letter-spacing: -0.002em;
  max-width: 44ch;
  margin: 0 0 clamp(32px, 4vw, 44px);
  position: relative;
}
.problem-pivot-lead {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-right: 8px;
  color: var(--terracotta);
  font-weight: 400;
}

/* CTA */
.problem-cta {
  align-self: flex-start;
  display: inline-block;
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  text-decoration: none;
  color: var(--cream);
  background: var(--terracotta);
  padding: 18px 44px;
  transition: background 0.3s var(--ease-premium), transform 0.2s var(--ease-premium);
}
.problem-cta:hover {
  background: var(--espresso);
}
.problem-cta:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid var(--terracotta);
  outline-offset: 3px;
}
.problem-cta:active {
  transform: scale(0.98);
}

/* Responsive */
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .problem-inner {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: clamp(32px, 6vw, 56px);
  }
  .problem-media img {
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    max-height: 440px;
  }
  .problem-cta {
    align-self: stretch;
    text-align: center;
  }
}
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Problem Section",
  "presets": [{ "name": "Problem Section" }]
}
{% endschema %}
